        // About
        section#about.page-section
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase About
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted Discover the story of our journey.
                ul.timeline
                    li
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/1.jpg', alt='...')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 July 2017
                                h4.subheading Our Humble Beginnings
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | We published ApexCharts.js and it's surrounding libraries which quickly became one of the most popular solutions for building charts on the web.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/2.jpg', alt='...')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 March 2021
                                h4.subheading A Firm is Born
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | Vizograph Solutions was officially launched, offering specialized data visualization services.
                    li
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/3.jpg', alt='...')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 October 2022
                                h4.subheading Transition to Full Service
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | In addition to data visualization, we began incorporating AI to generate more profound insights from your data.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            h4
                                | Be Part
                                br
                                | Of Our
                                br
                                | Story!

